Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.44,0:00:33.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這麼早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.70,0:00:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.01,0:00:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.85,0:00:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.35,0:00:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.42,0:00:56.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.92,0:01:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉把你拉了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.09,0:01:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是觀櫻花的名勝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.94,0:01:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.54,0:01:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還記得我之前說的話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.37,0:02:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我一定要去那所大學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.59,0:02:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為那所大學是我的父母相遇的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.45,0:02:19.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我也覺得能在那裡遇見一個出色的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.11,0:02:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經找到了 出色的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.41,0:02:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以再和你一起吃飯嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.08,0:02:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以再和你一起去澡堂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在未來的時間裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以和你一直在一起嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:34.11,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}目の前の扉を開けたら春風
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:37.53,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}鳥たちも樹木で待ち合わせ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:42.28,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}君へ向かう信号は青空色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:44.45,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}駆けだせばいい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:47.49,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}嘘つき確率論とか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:51.04,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}1+1=∞とか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:56.00,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}教えてくれた君と探しに行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:59.63,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}春待ちクローバー
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:34.11,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}打開面前的門迎來春風
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:37.53,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}鳥兒們在樹上等候著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:42.28,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}通往你的信號顯示著天藍色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:44.45,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}筆直向前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:47.49,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}說謊機率論啦
